      "rationale": "All three FEA solvers (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) are covered by documented quality management systems. Ansys holds ISO 9001 certification; FDA in-house code is governed by CDRH software QA procedures. Gradation 3 achieved: formal SQA plan with regression testing in place."
