      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of model setup by a second analyst; documented checklist covering boundary conditions, material assignments, and load application.",
      "rationale": "A peer-review checklist was completed by a second FEA engineer not involved in model construction. Boundary conditions, material property assignments, and contact definitions were independently verified. No discrepancies found. Gradation 2 achieved."
