      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from certified coupon testing of the same titanium alloy lot used in bench specimens; geometric dimensions from CMM measurement of physical implants.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V material properties (E=114 GPa, σ_y=880 MPa) derived from tensile coupon tests on the same material lot. Screw and rod geometry verified by CMM to ±0.01 mm. UHMWPE block properties taken from manufacturer data sheet with ±10% sensitivity bounds evaluated. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
