      "rationale": "All FEA inputs (geometry, material properties, boundary conditions, fixture stiffness) were mapped to experimentally measured values. Maximum discrepancy was 3.1% for UHMWPE compressive modulus. Fixture compliance was characterized and incorporated into the model. Gradation 3 achieved."
