      "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed available validation metrics. Structured level data for this factor were not finalized at the time of package submission pending inter-laboratory reconciliation of force-displacement curve alignment. The factor is considered assessed based on qualitative review of preliminary results, which indicate agreement within expected bounds."
