      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs mandated by ASTM F1717 and referenced in FDA guidance for pedicle screw 510(k) submissions. Direct traceability to clinical performance (subsidence risk, fatigue life) is documented in the COU description. Gradation 3 achieved."
