      "rationale": "The validation activity directly mirrors the COU: identical non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw geometry, ASTM F1717 compression-bending loading mode, and UHMWPE vertebral body surrogate. No surrogate geometry substitutions were made. Inter-laboratory testing at two independent sites strengthens confidence in result generalizability. Gradation 3 achieved."
